## Environment variables

These are some of the environment variables available in templates during
init.


Key                            | Value
-------------------------------|-------------------
`GITHUB_USER`                  | `<|GITHUB_USER|>`
`LOCAL_KEY`                    | `<|LOCAL_KEY|>`
`VENDOR_DEFINED`               | `<|VENDOR_DEFINED|>`

Key                            | Value
------------------------------ |-------------------
`PROJECT_NAME`                 | `<|PROJECT_NAME|>`
`PROJECT_IDENTIFIER`           | `<|PROJECT_IDENTIFIER|>`
`PROJECT_DOWNCASE_IDENTIFIER`  | `<|PROJECT_DOWNCASE_IDENTIFIER|>`
`PROJECT_UPCASE_IDENTIFIER`    | `<|PROJECT_UPCASE_IDENTIFIER|>`
`PROJECT_LANGUAGE`             | `<|PROJECT_LANGUAGE|>`
`PROJECT_DIALECT`              | `<|PROJECT_DIALECT|>`

